
= a proposal circulated by David Bollier


=Description=

"I want to pursue two interrelated structural strategies:
 
            
1.  Introduce and propagate the new/old “meta-language” of the commons. 
                 
The goal is to validate a new discourse of governance that can transcend the limits
of current political debate and open up a richer spectrum of possibilities; and
 
            
2.  Showcase how emerging digital technologies and platforms could expand
commons governance practices for natural resources at larger scales, beyond
the local (“eco-digital commons”), and mobilize new forms of collective action. 
                 
The goal is to demonstrate practical network-based alternatives to the market/state
and centrally directed regulation."



